"e":123.54,"text":"More than words that don’t do a thing"},{"s":123.96,"e":126.52,"text":"St. John needs one hundred million"},{"s":126.52,"e":129.82,"text":"One hundred million, right now"},{"s":130.58,"e":133.3,"text":"These people are people too"},{"s":133.56,"e":136.58,"text":"Don’t leave them standing down"},{"s":136.58,"e":140,"text":"St. John needs one hundred million"},{"s":140,"e":143.22,"text":"One hundred million, somehow"},{"s":144.1,"e":146.78,"text":"These people are people too"},{"s":147.16,"e":150.34,"text":"And we can help them now"},{"s":151.56,"e":154.56,"text":"This is not a small ask"},{"s":155.22,"e":158.1,"text":"This is hunger, this is home"},{"s":158.56,"e":161.2,"text":"This is dignity in daylight"},{"s":161.2,"e":164.9,"text":"For the ones who’ve walked alone"},{"s":164.9,"e":167.84,"text":"So raise it up, raise it up"},{"s":167.98,"e":170.58,"text":"Let the whole world hear the sound"},{"s":170.58,"e":177.06,"text":"One hundred million, one hundred million"},{"s":177.73,"e":183.48,"text":"For the hands that hold us down"},{"s":184.24,"e":187.26,"text":"St. John needs one hundred million"},{"s":187.26,"e":190.62,"text":"One hundred million, right now"},{"s":191.34,"e":194.04,"text":"These people are people too"},{"s":194.04,"e":197.38,"text":"Don’t leave them standing down"},{"s":198.22,"e":200.76,"text":"St. John needs one hundred million"},{"s":200.76,"e":204,"text":"One hundred million, somehow"},{"s":204.86,"e":207.52,"text":"These people are people too"},{"s":207.76,"e":210.96,"text":"And we can help them now"},{"s":211.62,"e":214.32,"text":"These people are people too"},{"s":214.88,"e":217.5,"text":"Let’s bring that money now"}],"duration":234.6,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.253Z","stats":{"whisperWords":336,"polishedWords":329,"matched":297,"matchRate":0.903}}